###Block: Long Descriptions, if you wish to include them
Acid Splash.MOD	DESC:You create an acidic bubble at a point within range, where it explodes in a 5-foot-radius Sphere. Each creature in that Sphere must succeed on a Dexterity saving throw or take ld6 Acid damage. &nl; Cantrip Upgrade. The damage increases by 1d6 when you reach levels 5 (2d6), 11 (3d6), and 17 (4d6).|!PRERULE:1,DisplayFullSpell
Aid.MOD	DESC:Choose up to three creatures within range. Each target's Hit Point maximum and current Hit Points increase by 5 for the duration. &nl; Using a Higher-Level Spell Slot. Each target's Hit Points increase by 5 for each spell slot level above 2.|!PRERULE:1,DisplayFullSpell	DESC:&nl; Material Component: a strip of white cloth.
Alarm.MOD	DESC:DESC:You create a magical alarm around a point within range. The spell alerts you when a creature enters the area of the spell.|!PRERULE:1,DisplayFullSpell